This is going the be the first stop for all interested in theoretical physics. Whether you have been a victim of a poor education, fallen for a pseudointillectual grifter, are a student
looking for a deeper understanding for your coursework, or are simply a layperson interested in exploring these fascinating topics as a hobbiest, this is the place to start. 

After this foundational period, we will move forward witht the assumption that you have read and understood all of the information included here.
